{"tid":931292,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來我嘅毒氣係遺傳左我老竇","createTime":"2018-12-07T02:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T12:45:17.000Z","uid":63452,"like":74,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c02f0300c254875dd60ca449d61077b0f969099","tid":931292,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"話說前排U 記同Jump 合作出左一堆T shirt<br />\n話曬都係有返咁上下年資嘅動漫毒撚，我梗係要整返幾件啦<br />\n嗰日全家出街搭緊車立，我就拎左件Hunter x Hunter 黎著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://uniqlo.scene7.com/is/image/UNIQLO/goods_00_410903?$prod$\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funiqlo.scene7.com%2Fis%2Fimage%2FUNIQLO%2Fgoods_00_410903%3F%24prod%24&h=92032016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老竇望住我件T，不以為然咁問一句: <span style=\"color: red;\">呀仔乜你件嘢啲公仔咁似幽遊白書嘅？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/vocustaiwan/images/8/8a/幽遊白書.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20150803040511&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fvocustaiwan%2Fimages%2F8%2F8a%2F%E5%B9%BD%E9%81%8A%E7%99%BD%E6%9B%B8.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20150803040511%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=e2b6a938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽完呆撚左幾秒，即刻反問返佢轉頭: <span style=\"color: red;\">係呀，兩個同一個作者㗎嘛，你又會識嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老竇即刻扮無嘢望住個樓層層樓係到跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老母即係大大聲踢爆佢: <span style=\"color: red;\">佢以前呀睇卡通片睇到上曬腦㗎，我地結左婚嘈交呀，電視一播星矢佢即刻交都唔嘈住，坐係梳化睇完套嘢先再嘈過呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你老闆我以家廿幾歲我老竇都重成日叫我唔好睇埋啲 '無無謂謂嘅卡通片'，點知原來自己幾廿歲 仔女都生埋都重睇緊動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好在老母當場踢爆你，以後你再嘈我睇動畫我就有嘢反擊笑鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2951e08caa091098c24938224db07f704505f914","tid":931292,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"困𨋢？"},{"pid":"8e8fb0b319d293b0acf0d3b03b6b37490f5670ca","tid":931292,"uid":141869,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"7/10<br />\n雖有亮點,但較為平淡"},{"pid":"55ed9d24afa1430f0a562726664a1630127b426b","tid":931292,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"就係唔想你步佢後塵 叫你生性啊死仔"},{"pid":"bdec7a04df7d0d6110d70be55ac735778be5413e","tid":931292,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2951e08caa091098c24938224db07f704505f914","tid":931292,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"困𨋢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"個conversation 30 秒到啫<br />\n舊樓啲車立真係好慢，啲friend 黎親都屌曬鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45224149f322c730ef48531d67f1ca51608e83a","tid":931292,"uid":15,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"如果唔係你老母毒到都識埋星矢佢就唔會識到你老豆啦"},{"pid":"1586db6b550b620fc93c08d88845fc46df74e091","tid":931292,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45224149f322c730ef48531d67f1ca51608e83a","tid":931292,"uid":15,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"如果唔係你老母毒到都識埋星矢佢就唔會識到你老豆啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:41:25.000Z","msg":"耳儒目染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2907a5b993f25b8ace563039b5b54667ba007a31","tid":931292,"uid":131545,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:41:55.000Z","msg":"老豆咁毒都溝到你老母 證明毒撚都溝到女"},{"pid":"10880198db69dc94794b